2. Dynamic AIDS model

As mentioned, as a result of substantial increase in per capita income in rural China, the
consumption patterns have changed dramatically
for some food products in the last decade. The
theoretical model to be employed for this study
has to take into account these changes. Thus, the
model has to be able to capture the dynamic

