nature of the consumption parameters for Chinese rural households. In other words, the model
should have the ability to reflect the changes in
consumption patterns of the rural population.
However, due to data limitations and the aggregate nature of the data set, we cannot use formal
or conventional dynamic demand models. Therefore, the model should not only consider the
dynamic nature of the consumption patterns, but
also take into account the data limitations.
