household responsibility system are 14% in 1980, 45% in
1981, 80% in 1982, 98% in 1983, respectively (Lin, 1992).
6 According to Fan's estimation, the production efficiency
effects of the reforms were released through a period of time
(0.753 in 1980, 0.768 in 1981, 0.788 in 1982, 0.791 in 1983,
0.83.1 in 1984, and 0.843 in 1985). Only after 1984 and 1985
did the efficiency start to improve greatly.

